Project Summary:
The Sentiment Analysis Bot is a Python + Flask-based web application that
analyzes text, PDFs, images, and document inputs to classify sentiments
into Positive, Negative, Neutral, and Hate-Speech categories.
It leverages the BERT transformer model for NLP-based prediction and
includes real-time data visualization using Matplotlib.

